[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はあ、はあ……やった、倒せた……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00632",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "兄さん、大丈夫？　傷口……また開いてない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00633",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ああ、大丈夫だ。少なくとも生きてる……\n今はそれで十分だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00634",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "説得、できたのかな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00635",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "少なくとも、これくらいで済んだのなら\n１週間かけて準備した甲斐があったと思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00636",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "アタシの知ってる知識を総動員して作った\n諸島同盟旅のしおり、渡せなかった……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00637",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まあ、あの二人の場合、誰かのお仕着せじゃなくて\n自分で楽しみを探してるほうが性に合うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00638",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "これでしばらくは生き延びられる……\nとはいえ、あくまでしばらくの間だけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00639",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あの強さのドラゴンを軽く従えられる……\nやっぱり強いのね、ヘルトとゼロって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00640",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "うん。結局あの二人は楽しんでるのさ。\n本気を出せば僕らを軽々なぎ倒せるんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00641",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "すでにホルハーツとかは見物してたみたいだけど、\n読み通り島で騒ぎは起こしてない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00642",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "上機嫌で遊んでいる分には、大人しいはずだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00643",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "これで、二人の考えがこっちに寄ってくれたら言うこと\nないんだけどね。いつまで平和が続くことやら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00644",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "これからは一層気を引き締めて、\n「九偉人図」を集めなくちゃってことですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00645",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ああ、そうだったわ。次はベスティラよね？\nエルスとタイニーに会いに行かなきゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00646",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ブラオールの港に出発だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00647",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。でもその前に……ちょっとだけいい？\n改めてみんなに言っておきたいの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00648",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00649",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私の兄弟……九偉人は、パルメ族の指示で\n人間たちを「管理」しようとしている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00650",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でも、私はその「管理」に反対。\n九偉人も……パルメ族も、別に偉くもなんともない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00651",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "言い切ってくれるねぇ、まぁ同意さ。\n長く生きてるだけだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00652",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私はレスナの叶えたいことを手伝いたい……\nそう思ってたし、今も思ってる。でも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00653",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私にもやりたいことができた。兄弟のこと……\n九偉人の問題は私がけりを付けたいの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00654",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00655",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトの性格、見たでしょ？　あんな奴の親玉に\n「管理」なんてますます任せられないわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00656",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "キューンなんか、ずっと怯えちゃってたし。\n可哀そうに、そりゃあ、ああなるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00657",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん、まずはあの子のことを助けてあげたいわ。\n記憶にはないけど、かわいい妹なんだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00658",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "キューンは潜在能力がヘルトやゼロに\n匹敵するから、二人も目をかけてるんだろうね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00659",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "というか、末っ子の面倒を見ようと思ってるんだろう。\nヘル兄なりにさ。そういう兄貴っぽさはあるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00660",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ただ、暴君がすぎる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00661",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヴァレリアの思うまま、やりたいようにしなよ。\n何があっても、アタシはお前さんの味方だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00662",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ、ありがとう。\nなんだか……お姉ちゃんみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00663",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……ふ、なに言ってるんだい。\n本当に姉なんだから、当たり前だろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00664",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ふふ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00665",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "さて、色々片付いたところで、\nいよいよベスティラに行くわよ！　しゅっぱーつ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00666",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "みんな",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00667",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "カット",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00668",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "カット",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00669",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]